1. Vision Statement

For patients seeking medical care at a hospital who deals with lengthy waiting times and limited access to appointment booking services. The MyCare platform is an online appointment booking system that allows round-the-clock booking, reduces queue times and provide transparent scheduling.
Unlike the current walk-in-only system or calling to schedule an appointment, our product offers instantaneous booking confirmation, queue visibility and flexible appointment scheduling.

